item.title: 2 Servers in 1 ~ RuneFallen ~ 2 Servers in 1
item.dc:creator: @JavaTC JavaTC
item.description:
@JavaTC wrote:

[quote=“Aragornian, post:3, topic:447602”]1) Like I tell everyone else. Try it before commenting. Without trying you have absolutely no clue what has been changed/fixed/added.

  1. 98% of IPB/vBulletin forum associated with RSPS’s are nulled. Don’t tell me otherwise.

  2. Good luck with life.[/quote]

  3. Like I say, you’re Supposed to list what you’ve changed/added and other things that add appeal to advertisements, not say “hey guys hurhur come play me serba has loads of stuff dat no serba has!” When the “loads of stuff” turns out to be 4 shops. So basically, you’re saying that you either didn’t add anything new or you just don’t give enough of a shit to attract players that will actually stay.

  4. Servers that use ‘nulled’ IPB/vBForum are typically the ones that are hosted by kids who think that everything in life is free and aren’t willing to spend money on their server. Even if you have to use a free alternative such as smf for a while it’s better than showing that you aren’t actually willing to invest into your server. You could say “oh but it’s overpriced”, when you probably don’t know how much work actually goes into developing such forums and how reliable they can be.

  5. Go suck a fucking lemon.
